</head>

<body>

    <!-- Start Header/Navigation -->
    <nav class="custom-navbar navbar navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark bg-dark" arial-label="Furni navigation bar">

        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="index.html">Lson<span>.</span></a>

            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarsFurni" aria-controls="navbarsFurni" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarsFurni">
                <ul class="custom-navbar-nav navbar-nav ms-auto mb-2 mb-md-0">
                    <li class="active"><a class="nav-link" href="shop.html">Shop</a></li>
                    <li><a class="nav-link" href="about.html">About us</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div style="margin-left: 15px">
                    <form action="/Product/ShowCart">
                        <button style="border: none; background-color: transparent"><i style="font-size: 30px; color: white" class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i></button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-left: 15px">
                    <form action="/Login/Index">
                        <button style="border: none; background-color: transparent"><i style="font-size: 30px; color: white" class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket"></i></button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </nav>
    <!-- End Header/Navigation -->
    <form id="formCart" onsubmit="return checkToCart(event)" action="/Product/AddToCart">
        <div style="margin: 0 auto; width: 50%; height: 500px; margin-top: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; background-color: #89c3ad66; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 7px 7px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)">
            <img style="margin-left: 50px; margin-top: 15px; width: 30%; height: 45%" src="/images/cabypara.jpg" class="img-fluid product-thumbnail">
            <div style="margin-right: 50px; text-align: center">
                <h1 style="color: #3b5d50; margin-top: 70px">@ViewBag.detailProduct.ProductName</h1>
                <br></br>
                <h5>Origin: @ViewBag.detailProduct.CompanyName</h5>
                <br></br>
                <h6 style="color: grey">In stock: @ViewBag.detailProduct.UnitsInStock</h6>
                <h4 style="color: black">$: @ViewBag.detailProduct.UnitPrice</h4>
                <h5>Quantity: <input style="width: 20%" type="number" name="quantity" id="inputQuantity"/></h5>
                <h6 id="msgErrQuantity" style="color: red"></h6>
                <input type="hidden" name="idProduct" value="@ViewBag.detailProduct.ProductId"></input>
                <input type="hidden" name="check" value="1"></input>
                <button onclick="checkToCart(event)">Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
    <div style="width: 3%; margin: 0 auto; margin-top: 15px">
        <a href="/Product/ShowProductPage" style=" text-decoration: none; color:#3b5d50; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold">Back</a>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Start Footer Section -->
    <footer class="footer-section">
        <div class="container relative">
            <div class="row g-5 mb-5">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="mb-4 footer-logo-wrap"><a href="#" class="footer-logo">Lson<span>.</span></a></div>
                    <p class="mb-4">Donec facilisis quam ut purus rutrum lobortis. Donec vitae odio quis nisl dapibus malesuada. Nullam ac aliquet velit. Aliquam vulputate velit imperdiet dolor tempor tristique. Pellentesque habitant</p>

                    <ul class="list-unstyled custom-social">
                        <li><a href="#"><span class="fa fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></span></a></li>
                        <li><a href="#"><span class="fa fa-brands fa-twitter"></span></a></li>
                        <li><a href="#"><span class="fa fa-brands fa-instagram"></span></a></li>
                        <li><a href="#"><span class="fa fa-brands fa-linkedin"></span></a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <div class="row links-wrap">
                        <div class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><a href="#">About us</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
                                <li><a href="#">Contact us</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-6 col-sm-6 col-md-3">
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li><a href="#">Support</a></li>
